casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Taylor. In re Taylor.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Taylor (1990), 49 Ohio St. 3d 605.]

(Nos. 89-2187 and 89-1613 Submitted February 7, 1990 Decided February 21, 1990.)

The resignation of Jonathan S. Taylor as an attorney is accepted. In view of Taylor’s submission of his affidavit of resignation, case No. 89-1613 is dismissed as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur,
